message.body: OMG I totally just realized that Saturday jay and I are celebrating our anniversary and making a trip to the wedding venue. We have to leave at 5:00, so if it's ok, your visit will have to be no more than an hour. Is that ok?
Yay congrats! No problem, I can probably come a little earlier or Sunday if any of that is easier?
We could do noon on Sunday!
So we're doing stand up paddle boarding Sunday morning and couldn't get there til later, 2ish? Or just stick to the Saturday plan? Busy busy!
